snippet: Canada's Milos Raonic is the fourth player to qualify for the ATP World Tour Finals in London following his run to the semi-finals in Beijing this week....
lead_paragraph: Canada's Milos Raonic is the fourth player to qualify for the ATP World Tour Finals in London following his run to the semi-finals in Beijing this week.

headline.print_headline: Raonic Confirms Spot in ATP World Tour Finals
headline.main: Raonic Confirms Spot in ATP World Tour Finals
